author: Doug P.
title: Doggone it, he doesn’t like her: Comedian-turned-senator finds Betsy DeVos ‘not qualified’
text:
Doggone it, he doesn’t like her: Comedian-turned-senator finds Betsy DeVos ‘not qualified’ Posted at 10:48   Doug P. Share on Facebook Share on Twitter 
Donald Trump’s nominee for Secretary of Education, Betsy DeVos, was questioned yesterday at her confirmation hearing, and Minnesota Senator and SNL alum Al Franken has made up his mind: It's clear that Betsy DeVos is not qualified for the job of @usedgov Sec., & I will not be supporting her nomination https://t.co/3cXbnzXCvD 
— Sen. Al Franken (@SenFranken) January 19, 2017 
And doggone it, he doesn’t like her. if she had just been a comedian instead…. https://t.co/LCxrryuLgJ 
— Deplorable Prez (@prezprobs) January 19, 2017 
Maybe things would have gone differently. Crazy, right? The next thing you know they'll elect a comedian with no political experience to the Senate after a sketchy recount. https://t.co/z51PYkgicd 
— Whig Over Easy (@rhinocartoon) January 19, 2017 But a TV writer is "qualified" to be a Senator?* 
* provided your friendly Secretary of State has an extra bag of votes or two https://t.co/QqSxz8Rlkp
